{"tid":1649994,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（勸世）若嘉年華式抗爭再現 大家就準備接受慘敗","createTime":"2019-10-12T19:23:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T19:32:56.000Z","uid":39215,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b0c1835be9fdb4e60cf3b05910cd7fd9fd0f7a13","tid":1649994,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:23:06.000Z","msg":"14年嘉年華式抗爭<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20141009/photo/bkn-20141009214749953-1009_00822_001_01p.jpg?20141010053619\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20141009%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20141009214749953-1009_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20141010053619&h=da6319cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/1024/201410/20141006104702_1_dcmn1005642_20141006_L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2F1024%2F201410%2F20141006104702_1_dcmn1005642_20141006_L.jpg&h=66d30d90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後果：第一次慘敗 無限政治打壓 <br />\n香港人變番港豬 政府當香港人係狗咁侮辱 任意DQ <br />\n外國記者馬凱無故被取消visa 本土派全面被清算 雙普選仍不了了知<br />\n<br />\n19年<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4xtjr6G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4xtjr6G.png&h=63568bbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BOeVKPZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBOeVKPZ.jpg&h=9f809d4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後果：<br />\n幾千位手足被捕 將會有幾百人被告暴動<br />\n已經有起碼十位手足自殺<br />\n無數手足可能&quot;被自殺&quot;<br />\n仲有爆眼 俾槍射 俾黑幫斬個班手足既付出將會白費<br />\n可以預想香港將會慘過新疆<br />\n<img src=\"https://n.kinliu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/tst.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.kinliu.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2Ftst.jpg&h=58a4ef52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/660/cpsprodpb/1D77/production/_107834570_hi054670827.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F660%2Fcpsprodpb%2F1D77%2Fproduction%2F_107834570_hi054670827.jpg&h=16f999e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://scd.cn.rfi.fr/sites/chinese.filesrfi/imagecache/rfi_16x9_1024_578/sites/images.rfi.fr/files/aefimagesnew/aef_image/xg_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fscd.cn.rfi.fr%2Fsites%2Fchinese.filesrfi%2Fimagecache%2Frfi_16x9_1024_578%2Fsites%2Fimages.rfi.fr%2Ffiles%2Faefimagesnew%2Faef_image%2Fxg_0.jpg&h=e7443af8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">若嘉年華式抗爭再現 香港將會萬劫不復。</span><br />\n<br />\n請大家去推行動post"},{"pid":"36793e2a8a33d905362fd58d46d2e5e98f943e93","tid":1649994,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:23:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">望諸君聽小弟一言</span>"},{"pid":"9f5e02f9f9db902268d36ce85f7f72df1c2405af","tid":1649994,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:24:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ce2525ad1642c332378f3604556bbce43a7a271","tid":1649994,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:25:17.000Z","msg":"咁我下次唔做前線<br />\n落去行到最前打卡返屋企睇直播算<br />\n當有一日我地贏左<br />\n我地相約煲底一齊慶祝！！"},{"pid":"89c5f6c4ee39a21bc4647abc99664a19f6a9839c","tid":1649994,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:25:20.000Z","msg":"希望唔會再有嘉年華式抗爭"},{"pid":"2ec59e5dd4a545abab92ca3d40fefebd06c310d1","tid":1649994,"uid":268619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:26:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">同佳戴綠帽</span>&gt;<span style=\"font-size: small;\">林鄭送中</span>&gt;<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">200萬人</span>&gt;<span style=\"font-size: large;\">警暴白色恐怖</span>&gt;<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">14億護旗手無NBA睇</span>&gt;<span style=\"font-size: small;\">港女食蛋糕分化全世界</span>&gt;<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">抗爭輸左</span></strong></span